# Snyk (https://snyk.io) policy file
# This file documents known, reviewed vulnerabilities that are accepted risks.
#
# All vulnerabilities below are transitive dependencies of react-scripts@5.0.1
# (a BUILD-TIME tool). They do NOT affect the production runtime because:
#   - react-scripts is only used during `npm run build`
#   - The production image runs nginx serving static HTML/JS/CSS
#   - None of these packages are shipped to end users
#
# These will be resolved when react-scripts is upgraded to v6+
# Review date: 2026-04-13

